   ```java
   @Query("SELECT e FROM Entity e WHERE e.id > :lastId ORDER BY e.id")
   List<Entity> findNextPage(@Param("lastId") Long lastId, Pageable pageable);
   ```

2. **Service Layer**:
   In your service, handle the pagination logic.

