To fix the infinite loop caused by an effect updating a signal, avoid writing to signals directly within effects, as this creates a circular dependency. Instead, use `untracked()` to read the signal without tracking it. Alternatively, restructure your logic to use `computed()` for derived values, which automatically updates when dependencies change without causing side effects.

